{"tid":288570,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"你係咪開我波?","createTime":"2017-06-18T09:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T08:27:33.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79ba4fae272e7dd59a9ad93e10a9bbf9a25d7977","tid":288570,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"放馬過黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efccb88a14dd85db1d44ddb3e78cee38d4a9c465","tid":288570,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"b50e419946e354aa1ed2f1d326006905c256781a","tid":288570,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:45:32.000Z","msg":"成班係度旁敲側擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7919cdd64f12e9f9e27b3ef55036e75180651a0","tid":288570,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想我嬲？</span></span>"},{"pid":"36ceeac41df4b859673930ee69047aa9f144a64b","tid":288570,"uid":100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:48:15.000Z","msg":"樓主又想被咬"},{"pid":"08495e6aa9dffa2021d5863719707681c7398c79","tid":288570,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"由於會員S_Kagawa撩鬼攞命，我宣布繼續！<br />\n<br />\n呢度對某一件事只可以有一種感覺，其他感覺就係on9！<br />\nC朗唔慶祝係100%高尚的丶有顧念的丶無私的，違背這意見的就唔得！<br />\n所有本區的會員思想要一致，正如北韓人民對金氏家族的崇拜一樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以字詞的定義要有一致性的標準，例如25的定義不可與官方有異，否則又係on9!<br />\n我平時圍內有十個朋友，有九個都話林峯好靚仔，但有一個話佢唔靚仔！豈有此理，林峯都叫唔靚仔？真係on9!我認為思想是要控制的，於是我們九位一齊圍插佢，話比佢知呢個世界只容許一種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc707a64c6b8662fea8a085e